          "tz": 480
        },
        "committer": {
          "name": "Liang Zhen",
          "email": "liang@whamcloud.com",
          "date": "2012-05-26 06:48:11.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-56 ptlrpc: clean up ptlrpc history",
        "message": "LU-56 ptlrpc: clean up ptlrpc history\n\nEach ptlrpc service is using service::srv_hist_lock to serialize\nall operations on history requests. In current implementation all\nrequests will be enqueued to history list while incoming and dequeued\nfrom history list on freeing, no matter RPC history is enabled or\ndisabled. This is unnecessary because RPC history is disabled by\ndefault, user enables it for only for problem diagnosis.\nThis patch will bypass history list operations if RPC history is\ndisabled, it will avoid performance issues on partitioned ptlrpc\nservice in the future.\n\nSigned-off-by: Liang Zhen <liang@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ic51b12c77ac8cac13912f0db60060cd987e6029f\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
